'''阿里·蘇利曼'''（{{lang-ar|علي سليمان}}，{{lang-he|עלי סלימאן}}，{{bd|1977年|10月10日}}）是一名[[阿拉伯裔以色列人|阿拉伯裔以色列]]男演員<ref name=yr20081028>{{cite web|title=Ali Suliman|url=http://1001-interviews.blogspot.com/2008/10/ali-suliman.html|work=1001 FILMS|publisher=Yama Rahimi|author=Yama Rahimi|quote=I usually get in trouble when I travel to an Arab country because I have an Israeli passport. So for them I'm not a Palestinian but an Israeli. I can't travel to certain Arab countries because they haven't recognized Israel despite being a Palestinian which is the most complicated thing.|date=2008-10-28|accessdate=2021-04-10|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402104015/http://1001-interviews.blogspot.com/2008/10/ali-suliman.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sanadfilmfund.com/en/archive/2014/10-29-Interview-with-actor-Ali-Suliman|title=Interview with actor Ali Suliman|website=sanadfilmfund.com|access-date=2019-01-05|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410083838/http://www.sanadfilmfund.com/en/archive/2014/10-29-Interview-with-actor-Ali-Suliman|dead-url=no}}</ref>，知名於電影《[[天堂不遠|天堂不遠]]》（2005年）和電視劇《[[湯姆克蘭西傑克萊恩|湯姆克蘭西傑克萊恩]]》（2018年）。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://fridaymagazine.ae/life-culture/people-profiles/ali-suliman-i-just-don-t-want-to-be-boring-1.2271249|title=Ali Suliman: I just don’t want to be boring|website=fridaymagazine.ae|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410083844/https://fridaymagazine.ae/life-culture/people-profiles/ali-suliman-i-just-don-t-want-to-be-boring-1.2271249|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://gulfnews.com/entertainment/meet-the-arab-actors-of-tom-clancys-jack-ryan-1.2272705|title=Meet the Arab actors of ‘Tom Clancy’s Jack Ryan’|website=gulfnews.com|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410083840/https://gulfnews.com/entertainment/meet-the-arab-actors-of-tom-clancys-jack-ryan-1.2272705|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 生平 ==
阿里·蘇利曼出生於以色列[[拿撒勒|拿撒勒]]。他畢業於{{lang|en|Yoram Loewenstein}}表演學校，並在劇院開始了他的事業。2005年，他在巴勒斯坦電影《[[天堂不遠|天堂不遠]]》中擔任主角；該片贏得[[金球獎最佳外語片|金球獎最佳外語片]]並入圍[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]的同一類別。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.goldenglobes.com/film/paradise-now|title=Golden Globe Awards for 'Paradise Now'|website=goldenglobes.com|access-date=2019-01-07|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803115614/https://www.goldenglobes.com/film/paradise-now|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在美國電影中，他出演的作品如《[[反恐戰場|反恐戰場]]》（2007年）、《[[謊言對決|謊言對決]]》（2008年）和《[[孤独的生还者|孤独的生还者]]》（2013年）。也曾參演破受好評的以色列電影《{{le|檸檬樹 (電影)|Lemon Tree (film)|檸檬樹}}》（2008年）。2018年，蘇利曼在[[Amazon_Prime_Video|Amazon Prime Video]]電視劇《[[湯姆克蘭西傑克萊恩|湯姆克蘭西傑克萊恩]]》第一季中飾演大反派穆薩·賓·蘇萊曼（{{lang|en|Mousa bin Suleiman}}），是與美國作對的[[葉門|葉門]]恐怖份子領導者<ref>{{cite news|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|title=''Jack Ryan'': Wendell Pierce, Dina Shihabi and Ali Suleiman Cast In Amazon Series|url=https://deadline.com/2016/12/jack-ryan-wendell-pierce-dina-shihabi-and-ali-suliman-cast-amazon-series-1201872535/|accessdate=2017-10-08|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2016-12-16|archive-date=2021-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210410083835/https://deadline.com/2016/12/jack-ryan-wendell-pierce-dina-shihabi-and-ali-suliman-cast-amazon-series-1201872535/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；隨後又在[[Hulu|Hulu]]迷你剧《[[巨塔杀机_(迷你剧)|巨塔杀机]]》中飾演卡米甚將軍（{{lang|en|General Qamish}}）。

